data.description: Situated in the heart of a sought-after neighborhood, this home offers the perfectblend of sophistication and convenience. This 4 bedroom and 2.5 bathroom home offers an unparalled living experience. The custom chef kitchen comes with quartz countertops, a potfiller, custom cabinets, and a large center island that invites culinary creativity. Enjoy the abundance of space in the family room with high ceilings and sky lights perfect for entertaining and everyday living. Second floor offers 4 generously sized bedrooms and a bathroom with heated floors. To take it to the next level,the master suite is a true oasis complete with 2 walk-in closets and a spa-like ensuite bathroom w/heated floors. Home includes plenty of storage and a spacious garage ensuring your living spaces remain clutter-free. Benefit from the community's amenities such as parks, recreational facilities, shopping districts, and excellent schools, all within close proximity. Home located with easy access to major highways, public transportation, and a range of dining and entertainment options perfectly positioned for enjoyment and leisure. Seize the opportunity to own this remarkable home that seamlessly blends luxury, functionality, and style.
